com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common

Class Page

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epimorphics.rdfutil.RDFNodeWrapper
      • com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common.CommonNodeWrapper
        • com.epimorphics.lda.renderers.common.Page

  • public class Page
extends CommonNodeWrapper
    Value object representing the page of results returned by Elda's query processing. Corresponds to a single resource of type api:Page.
    Author:
    Ian Dickinson, Epimorphics (mailto:ian@epimorphics.com)
